\v 1 While Peter and Yohan were still talkingВҰ83980 to the people, the chiefВҰ83992 priestsВҰ83992 and a templeВҰ83998 officerВҰ83996 and some people from the Sadducee sect approachedВҰ83989 them
\v 2 becauseВҰ84007 they were very upset about what they'd been teachingВҰ84009 the peopleВҰ84012, including preachingВҰ84015 thatВҰ84026 \nd YeshuaВҰ84019\nd* could give life to the deadВҰ84029.
