\v 9 if we're beingВҰ84152 questioned todayВҰ84151 about a goodВҰ84156 deed done to a manВҰ84157 who couldn't walk and which resulted in his healing,
\v 10 then you all need to know, and the peopleВҰ84172 of Yisrael shouldВҰ84165 also know, that it was done under the authority and name of \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ84179\nd*. He was the man from \nd NazarethВҰ84181\nd* that you executedВҰ84184 on a pole, butВҰ84168 who \nd GodВҰ84187\nd* brought back to life. It was because of his authority that this man can now stand beforeВҰ84195 you without deformity.
\v 11 \x + \xo 4:11: \xt Psa 118:22.\x*This Yeshua is:
