\q1 has now becomeВҰ84212 the \add vital\add* cornerstoneВҰ84215.вҖҷ
\m
\v 12 We can'tВҰ84221 be saved by anyoneВҰ84221 else, becauseВҰ84227 there'sВҰ84231 no otherВҰ84220 nameВҰ84229 or authority that's been givenВҰ84239 in the entire world underВҰ84234 which peopleВҰ84241 can be saved.
