\v 13 The assembled leaders were amazedВҰ84264 when they saw the boldnessВҰ84253 of PeterВҰ84252 andВҰ84249 Yohan who they knew to be illiterateВҰ84260, working-class menВҰ84259 ThenВҰ84249 they recognisedВҰ84265 that they'd been with \nd Yeshua\nd*,
