\p
\v 23 After Peter and Yohan had been released, they wentВҰ84464 to theirВҰ84466 own \add group\add* and told them what the chiefВҰ84475 priestsВҰ84475 and eldersВҰ84478 had saidВҰ84479.
\v 24 \x + \xo 4:24: \xt Exo 20:11; Neh 9:6; Psa 146:6.\x*WhenВҰ84481 they all heardВҰ84482 this, they began to pray out loud to \nd GodВҰ84494\nd*, saying, вҖңYahwehВҰ84497, youВҰ84498 created heavenВҰ84504 and earthВҰ84507 and the seaВҰ84510, and everything in them.
\v 25 \x + \xo 4:25-26: \xt Psa 2:1-2 (LXX).\x*You spoke \add long ago\add* by the holy \nd spiritВҰ84522\nd* through ourВҰ84520 ancestor who was yourВҰ84531 servantВҰ84530, DavidВҰ84528, when youВҰ84531 saidВҰ84532,
