\m
\v 27 \x + \xo 4:27: a \xt Luk 23:7-11; \xo b \xt Mat 27:1-2; Mrk 15:1; Luk 23:1; Yhn 18:28-29.\x*And indeed HerodВҰ84580 and PontiusВҰ84583 PilateВҰ84584 met with the paganВҰ84586 \add Romans\add* and the peoplesВҰ84588 of Yisrael to conspire againstВҰ84571 yourВҰ84575 holy servantВҰ84574 \nd Yeshua\nd* who you chose.
