\p
\v 31 As they finished theirВҰ84651 requests, the placeВҰ84654 where they had met was shakenВҰ84652 and all of them were filledВҰ84660 with the holy \nd spiritВҰ84667\nd*, and they \add went out and\add* boldly proclaimed God's messageВҰ84671.
