\p
\v 32 \x + \xo 4:32: \xt Acts 2:44-45.\x*And so the group of believersВҰ84684 were united in their will andВҰ84681 attitude. No one claimed anythingВҰ84703 to be their own, butВҰ84714 they shared everything they had.
