\p
\v 1 But in contrast, a couple named AnaniasВҰ84832 and SapphiraВҰ84836 sold a propertyВҰ84841
\v 2 butВҰ84842 agreed together to hide some of the proceeds. So Ananias broughtВҰ84854 a smaller amount and put itВҰ84862 down in front of the missionaries.
\v 3 Then PeterВҰ84867 saidВҰ84864, вҖңAnaniasВҰ84870, why has SatanВҰ84878 filledВҰ84874 yourВҰ84881 mindВҰ84880 such that you would lie to the holy \nd spiritВҰ84885\nd* and keep aside some of the proceeds of the propertyВҰ84896?
\v 4 Wasn't it yours before it was sold? And even when it was sold, the money was still yours. Why did you decideВҰ84913 to handle it like this? It wasn't peopleВҰ84925 that you're lyingВҰ84924 to, butВҰ84904 \nd GodВҰ84928\nd*.вҖқ
\v 5 WhenВҰ84931 AnaniasВҰ84933 heard that, he fell down andВҰ84931 stoppedВҰ84939 breathingВҰ84939. Everyone who heard about it felt very afraid,
\v 6 and the youngВҰ84952 menВҰ84952 there stood up and coveredВҰ84953 his \add body\add*, carried it out, and buriedВҰ84957 him.
\p
\v 7 Three hoursВҰ84962 later, Ananias' wifeВҰ84967 came in, not knowingВҰ84970 anything aboutВҰ84961 what had happened.
\v 8 PeterВҰ84981 checked, вҖңIs it true that youВҰ84992 guys sold the propertyВҰ84990 for such-and-such an amount?вҖқ
\p вҖңYes, for that amount,вҖқ sheВҰ84993 replied.
\p
\v 9 ButВҰ85029 PeterВҰ85001 saidВҰ85001 to her, вҖңWhy did the two of you agreeВҰ85008 to test \nd Yahweh's spiritВҰ85013\nd*? The guys who just buriedВҰ85020 yourВҰ85023 husbandВҰ85022 are just out the doorВҰ85027, and they'll carry you out as well.вҖқ
\v 10 Sapphira immediatelyВҰ85035 fell down in front of himВҰ85040 and stoppedВҰ85042 breathingВҰ85042. ThenВҰ85034 the youngВҰ85046 menВҰ85046 came in and foundВҰ85047 her deadВҰ85049, so they took \add her body out\add* and buriedВҰ85055 her with her husbandВҰ85058.
\v 11 SoВҰ85060 the entireВҰ85065 assemblyВҰ85067 of believers becameВҰ85061 very afraid, along with everyone else who heard about theseВҰ85074 events.
\s1 Ongoing miracles and healings
