\p
\v 12 The missionaries went on to do many miracles and amazing things, and all the peopleВҰ85091 who gathered in Solomon'sВҰ85105 Porch had a united vision,
\v 13 butВҰ85115 no one else dared to join them. However, the peopleВҰ85119 were talking positively about them
\v 14 and more were becoming believersВҰ85124 in the \nd masterВҰ85126\nd*вҖ”big numbers of both men and womenВҰ85131.
\v 15 Some would even bringВҰ85138 those who were sickВҰ85140 out to the side of the road, lying them on beds and mats waiting for PeterВҰ85152 to come past so that \add even\add* his shadowВҰ85155 might touch them.
\v 16 More crowds were comingВҰ85170 from the towns around Yerushalem, bringingВҰ85182 those who were sickВҰ85183 and those tormentedВҰ85185 by demonsВҰ85189, and they were all getting healedВҰ85192.
\s1 The preachers get arrested but released again
