\q2 because his lifeВҰ88282 is beingВҰ88277 taken from the earthВҰ88280?вҖҷ
\p
\v 34 вҖңNow tell me,вҖқ saidВҰ88290 the official, вҖңwho was Yeshayah talking about? Was he talking about himselfВҰ88300 or someoneВҰ88304 else?вҖқ
