\v 15 After the readingsВҰ92125 from the Law and from the Prophets,\f + \fr 13:15 \ft The Hebrew Scriptures are divided into the Law, the Prophets, and the Writings.\f* the leadersВҰ92133 sentВҰ92131 a messenger over to them to ask, вҖңMen, brothersВҰ92138, if youВҰ92146 bring any messageВҰ92147 of encouragement for the congregation, please share itВҰ92152.вҖқ
