\v 22 After Saul was removedВҰ92266, God chose David to be their kingВҰ92274вҖ”the man of whom he said, вҖҳI foundВҰ92279 David the son of Yishay \add (Jesse)\add*, a man who wants to obey me andВҰ92265 do everything I ask.вҖҷ
