\p
\v 26 вҖңMen, brothersВҰ92361, descendantsВҰ92363 of AbrahamВҰ92364 andВҰ92365 others here who revereВҰ92370 \nd GodВҰ92372\nd*, the teaching about this salvationВҰ92379 has been sentВҰ92381 to us.
\v 27 The people of Yerushalem and their \add religious\add* leaders didn'tВҰ92394 recognise this \add Yeshua\add*, butВҰ92388 by their judgementВҰ92409 of him theyВҰ92410 fulfilledВҰ92410 the words of the prophetsВҰ92401 that are read everyВҰ92404 Rest Day.
