\v 46 But PaulВҰ92835 and BarnabasВҰ92838 respondedВҰ92839 boldlyВҰ92830, вҖңIt was necessaryВҰ92844 for God's messageВҰ92849 to be explained in the meeting hall to all of \add the Jews\add* firstВҰ92845. But since you are rejecting that teaching, you are all judgingВҰ92860 yourselvesВҰ92863 to be unworthy of living forever, so instead, we will \add now\add* share it with the non-Jews.
