\v 4 Nevertheless, the peopleВҰ93094 of the cityВҰ93096 were dividedВҰ93089вҖ”some agreeing with the \add strict\add* Jews, and others supporting the missionaries.
\p
\v 5 At one point, both the non-Jews and the strict Jews and theirВҰ93129 leaders got worked up enough to come in order to attack them and throwВҰ93132 rocksВҰ93132 to kill them.
