\v 11 The crowdВҰ93251 of people who saw what PaulВҰ93257 had done began to shout out in Lycaonian, вҖңThese two look like menВҰ93268, butВҰ93249 they're really godsВҰ93265 who have come down to us!вҖқ
\v 12 They called BarnabasВҰ93278 вҖҳZeusВҰ93279вҖҷ and called PaulВҰ93282 вҖҳHermasВҰ93283вҖҷ sinceВҰ93285 he was the main speaker.
