\p
\v 14 ButВҰ93331 when the missionaries BarnabasВҰ93330 and PaulВҰ93332 heardВҰ93325 what was going on, they tore their clothes \add in dismay\add* as they rushedВҰ93339 out into the crowdВҰ93344
\v 15 shouting, вҖңMen, why are you doingВҰ93353 all these things? We are only humansВҰ93360 just like all of you. We were bringing you the good message about abandoning these uselessВҰ93371 \add sacrifices\add* and turningВҰ93373 to the livingВҰ93379 \nd GodВҰ93377\nd* who made heavenВҰ93385 and the earthВҰ93388 and the seaВҰ93391 and everything in them.\x + \xo 14:15: \xt Exo 20:11.\x*
