\v 19 ButВҰ93472 some \add strict\add* Jews cameВҰ93465 over from \add Pisidian\add* AntiochВҰ93469 and IconiumВҰ93474 and were able to persuadeВҰ93482 the crowdsВҰ93486. They threw rocks at PaulВҰ93503 \add to kill him\add* and draggedВҰ93505 his body outsideВҰ93507 the cityВҰ93509 \add gates\add* thinkingВҰ93510 that he was dead.
