\v 22 There they strengthenedВҰ93566 the faithВҰ93577 of the believersвҖ”encouraging them to continue believing andВҰ93578 to expect that it's normal to endure a lot of suffering on the path to God's kingdomВҰ93590.
\v 23 They appointed some elders for \add each\add* assemblyВҰ93598, thenВҰ93594 they fasted andВҰ93594 prayedВҰ93600 for the eldersвҖ”asking the \nd masterВҰ93607\nd* that they believedВҰ93610 in to look after them.
\p
\v 24 After passing throughВҰ93613 PisidiaВҰ93617, theyВҰ93618 arrived at Pamfylia
