\p
\v 27 SoВҰ93655 when they arrivedВҰ93654, they gatheredВҰ93657 the assemblyВҰ93659 togetherВҰ93657 there and shared about what \nd GodВҰ93665\nd* had done with them and how he had openedВҰ93674 up the doorВҰ93677 of faithВҰ93678 to the non-Jews.
