\v 1 ThenВҰ93688 some \add people\add* came \add to Antioch\add* from YudeaВҰ93693 andВҰ93688 were teaching the believersВҰ93696 thatВҰ93707 according to Mosheh's teachings, you can'tВҰ93700 be savedВҰ93713 unless you've been circumcisedВҰ93702.
\v 2 This led to no end of argument and debateВҰ93721 between them and PaulВҰ93725 and BarnabasВҰ93728 until it was decided that the two of them and some otherВҰ93760 believers should go to Yerushalem to ask the missionaries and the eldersВҰ93771 there aboutВҰ93778 this issue.
\p
