\p
\v 4 WhenВҰ93810 they arrivedВҰ93809 in YerushalemВҰ93812, they were welcomed by the assemblyВҰ93821 and the missionaries and the eldersВҰ93827, and they explained how \nd GodВҰ93834\nd* had used them.
