\p
\v 6 SoВҰ93873 the missionaries andВҰ93876 the eldersВҰ93878 met separately in order to consider the matterВҰ93882 further.
\v 7 After a lot of debateВҰ93887, PeterВҰ93918 stoodВҰ93914 up and said, вҖңMen, brothersВҰ93924, all of you here know that some time back, \nd GodВҰ93936\nd* choseВҰ93934 me to be a mouthpieceВҰ93942 so that the non-Jews could hear the good message and believeВҰ93952.
