\v 12 The whole group sat in silenceВҰ94034, and thenВҰ94036 they listened to BarnabasВҰ94042 and PaulВҰ94045 as they described everything that \nd GodВҰ94052\nd* had done amongВҰ94056 the non-Jews through them, including miracles and amazing things.
