\v 22 So the missionaries and eldersВҰ94240 with all the assemblyВҰ94244 decided to choose some men to accompany PaulВҰ94254 and BarnabasВҰ94256 to AntiochВҰ94251, so they choseВҰ94245 YudasВҰ94257 (nicknamed BarsabbasВҰ94261) and SilasВҰ94264 who were leaders amongВҰ94268 the believersВҰ94270,
\v 23 This is what they wroteВҰ94271: This letter is from the missionaries and eldersВҰ94284, your brothers \add here in Yerushalem\add* to our non-Jewish fellow believersВҰ94287 in AntiochВҰ94291 and SyriaВҰ94294 and CiliciaВҰ94297.
