\v 29 you all must keep away from anything sacrificedВҰ94404 to idols, from \add eating or drinking\add* bloodВҰ94406 or strangledВҰ94409 animalsВҰ94409, and from sexualВҰ94411 immoralityВҰ94411. You will do well if you avoid these things. Farewell.
\p
