\p
\v 6 From there, theyВҰ94794 travelled throughВҰ94794 PhrygiaВҰ94797 andВҰ94798 the GalatiaВҰ94800 regionВҰ94801, after the holy \nd spiritВҰ94806\nd* prevented them from proclaiming the messageВҰ94810 in AsiaВҰ94815 \add Minor\add*.
\v 7 When they got to MysiaВҰ94821, they planned to go on into BithyniaВҰ94827, butВҰ94818 \nd Yeshua's spiritВҰ94835\nd* didn'tВҰ94831 let them,
