\v 10 SoВҰ94881 as a result of the visionВҰ94885, weВҰ94892 decided to go straight to MacedoniaВҰ94896, concludingВҰ94897 that \nd GodВҰ94902\nd* had calledВҰ94899 us to share the good message with them.
\s1 Lydia's enthusiasm at Philippi
