\v 31 вҖңBelieveВҰ95412 in the \nd masterВҰ95416 YeshuaВҰ95417\nd*,вҖқ they replied, вҖңthenВҰ95410 you andВҰ95410 yourВҰ95425 householdВҰ95424 can all be savedВҰ95420.вҖқ
\v 32 ThenВҰ95426 they explained the messageВҰ95430 about the \nd masterВҰ95433\nd* to him andВҰ95426 all those in hisВҰ95441 householdВҰ95440.
\v 33 Even though it was still the middle of the nightВҰ95451, he sponged theirВҰ95455 woundsВҰ95456, and thenВҰ95442 him and hisВҰ95467 household were all immersedВҰ95459 straight away.
\v 34 He took Paul and Silas up into his houseВҰ95479 and gave them a meal, and his whole household were happy because they now believedВҰ95492 in \nd GodВҰ95496\nd*.
\p
\v 35 The next dayВҰ95498 the magistrates sentВҰ95502 officialsВҰ95505 to tell the jailer to release Paul andВҰ95499 Silas.
